snippet.title: Slime MoriMori Dragon Quest: Shōgeki no Shippo Dan | Full Slimes, Monsters, Items | GBA | 4K 2160p
snippet.description:
My childhood. Save file from 10 years ago, haha.
Too bad I didn't know about the painting. We didn't have guides available 10 years ago.

Using VBA-M 2.1.4 (VisualBoyAdvance-M), could be some kind of new version of the old VisualBoyAdvance with better filter (graphics) xBRZ 6x

Original gameplay was 1080p, upscaled to 2160p for better Youtube frame/bitrate/quality.
